resourceAbstractObject.default: Data from the 'Thau coastal environment research observatory' (REC-THAU): Observatory for research in the coastal environment of the watershed and the Thau lagoon: weather-hydrology, physicochemical and biological parameters (lagoon and foreshore).. This observatory is part of the Montpellier Research Observatory of Environment (OSU OREME, oreme.org). It is labelized in the framework of SNO SOMLIT. It consists in different observing tasks: SOMLIT-Sète ; Thau lagoon monitoring ; Thau lagoon watershed.
